attachments.displayName: Pictured are ECS team members who supported NOAA during acceptance trials (Sept. 30 - Oct. 4) on the NOAA Ship REUBEN LASKER. During acceptance trials, every component of every system is evaluated and tested to ensure it was built satisfactorily. Everyone involved put in long hours for months leading up to the successful completion this significant milestone.
